{"tid":287513,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"(西藏jj)召集所有想去西藏嘅臉孔","createTime":"2017-06-17T12:51:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-30T06:52:08.000Z","uid":35620,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7533a98b4d9c6b7fe14ededadf7ff842558f529e","tid":287513,"uid":35620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T12:51:00.000Z","msg":"有冇人有興趣去色達同年保玉則<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n暫定會喺8月3號出發，13號回程。因為同行有巴打臨時請唔到假去唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家仲有3個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n8月3號搭飛機去到成都，之後係觀音橋、色達、佛學院、天葬台。<br />\n<br />\n其後會喺年保玉則徒步行同露營幾日（呢個係重點）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n九寨溝係行程之一，不過會再傾下天氣唔好嘅plan b。<br />\n<br />\n上面都係主要行程，有興趣嘅話喺度問又得，或者tg我: LiHKGTL"},{"pid":"aa28f2f2671cf13f650625fb95af1f365a891570","tid":287513,"uid":35620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T13:32:06.000Z","msg":"第一推，我哋有tg group㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05b58afc5b830344ad3f907c7784aa3dd87d88bb","tid":287513,"uid":26531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T13:32:16.000Z","msg":"如果9月就好啦"},{"pid":"29e2957e88fa2c8884cd2a073026016862644dd8","tid":287513,"uid":35620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T13:46:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果9月就好啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打8月唔得咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"5c3d0932ffad495ba53f54bc903e80e4e1a016bc","tid":287513,"uid":26531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T13:51:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果9月就好啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打8月唔得咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？</blockquote><br />\n應該最難請到假<br />\n我plan左9月但好難搵伴"},{"pid":"94597970c916d08deea14ddf65554c7e12a60a22","tid":287513,"uid":35620,"lik